  "description": "Demonstrates KV-first core mechanics: context budget detection, KVCC-strict remote prefill, KV artifact transfer over QUIC, and KV ancestor reuse across sessions. Two sequential runs on the same prompt: first run pays full prefill cost on the delegate node; second run hits the KV ancestor cache and bypasses remote prefill entirely.",
