    "KVCC strict: bit-exact KV transfer between nodes sharing model_arch_id, weights_id, tokenizer_id",
    "Budget detection: local_overbudget triggers automatic peer scoring and handoff",
    "Remote prefill: N1 (4k ctx) delegates to N3 (32k ctx), N1 decodes on GPU",
    "KV artifact persistence: kv_ref survives session boundary, reusable cross-session",
    "KV ancestor hit: second run attaches to prior KV state, skips remote prefill",
    "All decisions automatic: no user-facing configuration change between runs"
  ],
